Line13.6DE47: My mother started this damn ritual. I'm going to finish it. Meet me in the Mistral Woods.
Line17.6DE47: So we need blessed blood. Go back to your Prava. Get that blessing. Beg if you need to. Whatever it takes.
Line19.6DE47: You were--you were protecting me. I don’t want to hate you. I’m trying. I really am.
Line23.6DE47: The Horadrim hid a vault there. Finding it was her life’s work. So much for that.
Line25.6DE47: Maybe it will help with the ritual. If not, at least I can bury her where she’d want.
Line29.6DE47: I need time. I’m sorry. Just leave me.
Line9.6DE47: (sigh) We're going to make Lilith pay for what she’s done.
